Interface OS


  • interface OS
    Centralised location for constant string values that are used throughout the classes that implement this interface.

    References:
    Loosely based on the source code of the System Utils class of Apache Commons Lang library. [Online]. Available: https://github.com/apache/commons-lang/blob/master/src/main/java/org/apache/commons/lang3/SystemUtils.java
